From: Saleh <saleh@emergegcc.com>
Date: Sat, 11 Apr 2026 20:10:57 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Teacher view: add WhatsApp button to send each teacher their
 weekly schedule

- New buildTeacherMessage(tname) formats a weekly schedule message grouped
  by day, similar in tone to buildParentMessage. Lists each session as
  "HH:MM - Student Name (Car N)".
- New sendTeacherWhatsApp(tname) opens wa.me/<phone>?text=... in a new tab
  using the teacher's saved phone from the Teachers table.
- New sendAllTeacherMessages() opens one WhatsApp tab per eligible teacher
  (phone + at least one scheduled session this week), staggered 350ms apart.
- Teacher Weekly Report card now shows a green 'WhatsApp' button instead
  of the plain phone link. Header bar gets a 'Send all teachers (N)' bulk
  button on the right.
- Disabled state + toast guidance when a teacher has no phone, or has a
  phone but no sessions.
- Smoke test 17 confirms buildTeacherMessage produces a non-empty message
  for a teacher with sessions and returns null for an empty teacher.
  17/17 passing.
